quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  19,16,Ndipo kukumbukira nkhani ya Maria m’Buku! Pamene iye adasiya anthu ake ndi kupita kumalo a payekha kumbali ya ku m’mawa
  19,17,Ndipo iye adafunda nsalu kuti anthu asaone nkhope yake. Ife tidamutumizira iye Mzimu wathu umene udaoneka ngati munthu
  19,18,"Maria adati, “Mwini chisoni anditeteze ine kwa iwe! Ngati iwe umaopa Ambuye, ndisiye ndekha, usandiyandikire ayi.”"
  19,19,"Mngelo adati, “Ine ndine Mthenga wa Ambuye wako ndipo ndadza kudzakupatsa mwana wamwamuna woyera.”"
  19,20,"Maria adati, “Kodi ine ndidzabereka mwana bwanji pamene ine ndine wosakhudzidwa ndi mwamuna ndiponso si ndine wachiwerewere ayi?”"
  19,21,"Mngelo adati, “Ndi momwemo” Ambuye wako wanena kuti, “Zimenezo, kwa Ine, ndi zopepuka. Tidzamupanga iye kukhala chizindikiro kwa anthu ndi madalitso ochoka kwa Ife. Limeneli ndilo lamulo limene lalamulidwa.”"
  19,22,Ndipo iye adakhala ndi pakati ndipo adapita kumalo akutali
  19,23,"Ndipo ululu wa kubereka udamubwerera pamene adali patsinde pa mtengo wa tende ndipo adalira nati, “Kalanga ine, bola ndikadangofa zisanachitike izi chifukwa ndikadakhala woiwalidwa.”"
  19,24,"Kudabwera mawu kuchokera pansi oti: “Usadandaule ayi. Ambuye wako wakukonzera ka mtsinje kamene kalikuyenda ku mapazi ako.”"
  19,25,"“Ndipo gwedeza mtengo watendewu, iwo udzagwetsa zipatso za tende zaziwisi ndi zakupsa.”"
  19,26,"“Idya ndi umwe, kotero sangalala.” Ndipo ukakumana ndi munthu wina aliyense muuze kuti, “Ine ndalumbira kwa Mwini chisoni kusala chakudya ndipo sindidzayankhula ndi munthu wina aliyense lero.”"
  19,27,Ndipo iye adatenga mwana wake nanka naye kwa anthu ake amene adati kwa iye’ “Iwe Maria! Ndithudi iwe wabweretsa chinthu cha chilendo.”
  19,28,“Iwe mlongo wake wa Aroni! Atate wako sanali munthu wochita zoipa ndiponso Amayi ako sadali a chiwerewere.”
  19,29,"Maria adamuloza iye. Koma iwo adati, “Kodi ife tingayankhule ndi mwana wam’chikuta bwanji?”"
  19,30,"Mwanayo adati, “Ine ndine kapolo wa Mulungu. Iye wandipatsa ine Buku labwino ndipo wandisankha kukhala Mtumwi.”"
  19,31,“Madalitso ake ali pa ine kulikonse kumene ndingapite ndipo wandilamulira kuti ndikhale wopemphera ndi kupereka chaulere kwa anthu osauka nthawi yonse ya moyo wanga.”
  19,32,“Iye wandilamula kuti ndizilemekeza amayi anga ndipo sadandipange kukhala wamwano ndi woipa.”
  19,33,"Ndipo mtendere ukhale kwa ine patsiku limene ndidabadwa, ndi patsiku limene ndidzafa ndiponso pa tsiku limene ndidzaukitsidwa kwa akufa"
  19,34,"Ameneyo ndiye Yesu, mwana wa Maria. Liwu loonadi limene iwo ali kukayika"
  19,35,"Sizili zoyenera kuti Mulungu akhale ndi mwana wamwamuna! Iye ayeretsedwe ku zimenezo. Ngati Iye afuna chinthu, Iye amangonena kuti, “Chikhale” ndipo chimakhaladi"
  19,36,Ndithudi Mulungu ndi Ambuye wanga ndiponso Ambuye wanu. Kotero mpembedzeni Iye yekha. Imeneyo ndiyo njira
  19,37,"Koma magulu a Akhirisitu adasemphana maganizo pakati pawo. Koma pamene tsiku loopsa lidza, tsoka kwa anthu osakhulupirira"
  19,38,Kodi iwo adzaona ndi kumva momveka bwanji pa tsiku limene adzaonekera pa maso pathu! Koma anthu ochita zoipa lero ali mu chisokonezo choonekeratu
  19,39,"Achenjeze za tsiku limene adzanong’oneza bombono, pamene malamulo athu adzakwaniritsidwa ndipo pamene iwo ali nkuiwala ndi kusakhulupirira"
  19,40,Ndithudi Ife tidzatenga dziko lapansi ndi onse amene amakhala m’menemo. Ndi kwa Ife kumene onse adzabwezedwa